spec_data.Name: mediawiki-intersection
spec_data.Description:
Outputs a bulleted list of most recent items
residing in a category, or an intersection
of several categories.
DynamicPageList is another name for this extension.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 07:30:41 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Create a list of pages that are listed in a set of categories
